entries.quest_escort_d: Follow the freighter to it's destination. Keep it protected from any enemy fighter that might try to take it's cargo.
entries.quest_location_d: The freighters will be jumping into Corellia system and need to have their escort meet them. You will be supplied the arrival location of your assigned vessel. Meet the vessel at this location.
entries.quest_rendezvous_d: The freighter will not arrive until you are at the arrival location. This is to ensure that they have an escort the entire time they are in Corellian system.
entries.reason_1: We have to get this patrol done.  Black Epsilon squadron needs to know the enemy flight reports.
entries.reason_2: Command is waiting on these scans, lets get a move on.

entries.title: Corellia System: Protect the Imperial Freighters Duty
entries.title_d: Travel to the Corellia system and escort important Imperial military supplies that are being sent in from Naboo. These will help restock the military that is located on Talus. It is highly important that the cargo ships arrive at their destination safely and most importantly do not fall into Rebel hands.
